{"tid":1512491,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【金融戰線再展開！！】第三次全民撳錢 九月七號出糧換美金","createTime":"2019-08-28T02:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T12:20:56.000Z","uid":104803,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"4488087582723ea5821224a1327a543d61c15de7","tid":1512491,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">九月七號出糧換美金<br />\n九月七號出糧換美金<br />\n九月七號出糧換美金</span><br />\n<br />\n816各位巴絲非常努力 撳爆好多部ATM 銀行唱到無哂美金連散紙都要拎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有傳支銀要拎樓契去華僑永亨(新加坡資金）同日本銀行借美金黎頂 我地要再接再厲！！！唔知大家有無收到銀行推銷定存電話？ 有無見到立法會金融界張華峰議員提倡規管市民提款 ？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經證明撳錢比政府好大壓力！！！係機場之外<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另一粒春袋！！！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果林鄭真係宣布緊急狀態，根據法例第241章政府係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以名正言順凍結或者充公香港銀行所有資產！！！</span></span>再唔提款 遲D變哂共產黨資產啦!<br />\n<br />\n各位手足 仲等咩 前線手足被打到骨折 女仔比剝光豬 點忍呀 用撳錢打開戰線 快D去撳錢啦 撳到政府怕 撳到中資企業借唔到錢 撳到佢支爆！！！<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴都叫大家撳錢返屋企 仲駛諗？去馬啦！<br />\n<br />\n九月七號一齊撳 撳完貼圖上來  我地口號： <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撳剩一蚊 比支銀做帛金！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/091937_231b28440896515b1f8ee267b217f281.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F091937_231b28440896515b1f8ee267b217f281.png&h=fae8eee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/27/195002_7bd3871db3748fec13624166ca4fb30f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2F195002_7bd3871db3748fec13624166ca4fb30f.png&h=844216d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/093450_b4ebdcb97434658402