D去撳錢啦 撳到政府怕 撳到中資企業借唔到錢 撳到佢支爆！！！<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴都叫大家撳錢返屋企 仲駛諗？去馬啦！<br />\n<br />\n九月七號一齊撳 撳完貼圖上來  我地口號： <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撳剩一蚊 比支銀做帛金！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/091937_231b28440896515b1f8ee267b217f281.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F091937_231b28440896515b1f8ee267b217f281.png&h=fae8eee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/27/195002_7bd3871db3748fec13624166ca4fb30f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2F195002_7bd3871db3748fec13624166ca4fb30f.png&h=844216d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/093450_b4ebdcb974346584021bedb178c0a226.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F093450_b4ebdcb974346584021bedb178c0a226.png&h=92b1d68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/093535_21ed8bbc7e4f1c28f3db3993f249e6f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F093535_21ed8bbc7e4f1c28f3db3993f249e6f7.png&h=d6cc62ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/27/195630_8a8b75750eb80ce4402ac09df2efe939.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2F195630_8a8b75750eb80ce4402ac09df2efe939.png&h=c99007a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/27/195652_b6b27967082f3a7d983d471af033fa29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F27%